Class DssDocumentWrapper

java.lang.Object
org.digidoc4j.impl.asic.cades.DssDocumentWrapper
All Implemented Interfaces:
eu.europa.esig.dss.model.DSSDocument, Serializable
public class DssDocumentWrapper extends Object implements eu.europa.esig.dss.model.DSSDocument
A wrapper for DSSDocuments for capturing document name and mimetype updates, and for shielding the wrapped document from those changes.
